<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Espace Livreur — MenuCam</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css"/>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Bricolage+Grotesque:wght@700;800&display=swap');
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    body{font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a 0%,#1e293b 100%);min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1.5rem;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
    .card{background:#fff;border-radius:24px;padding:2.5rem 2rem;width:100%;max-width:400px;box-shadow:0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
    .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:2rem}
    .logo-icon{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F59E0B,#D97706);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1.5rem;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(245,158,11,0.4)}
    .logo-text{text-align:left}
    .logo-name{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:800;color:#111}
    .logo-sub{font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;font-weight:500}
    h1{font-family:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;color:#111;text-align:center;margin-bottom:.4rem}
    p.sub{font-size:14px;color:#6B7280;text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.75rem}
    .alert{background:#FEE2E2;color:#B91C1C;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border:1px solid #FECACA}
    .form-group{margin-bottom:1rem}
    label{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#374151;display:block;margin-bottom:5px}
    .input-wrap{position:relative}
    .input-wrap i{position:absolute;left:12px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);color:#9CA3AF;font-size:15px}
    input{width:100%;padding:11px 14px 11px 38px;border:1.5px solid #E5E7EB;border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s;background:#F9FAFB;color:#111}
    input:focus{border-color:#F59E0B;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(245,158,11,.12);background:#fff}
    .btn-submit{width:100%;padding:13px;background:#F59E0B;color:#111;border:none;border-radius:12px;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;transition:all .2s;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-top:.5rem;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(245,158,11,.35)}
    .btn-submit:hover{background:#D97706;transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(245,158,11,.45)}
    .divider{text-align:center;font-size:13px;color:#9CA3AF;margin:1.25rem 0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
    .divider::before,.divider::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:#E5E7EB}
    .info-box{background:#FEF3C7;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#92400E;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">🛵</div>
    <div class="logo-text">
      <div class="logo-name">MenuCam Livreur</div>
      <div class="logo-sub">Espace dédié aux livreurs</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h1>Connexion</h1>
  <p class="sub">Accédez à vos commandes et votre carte de livraison</p>
  <% if(error&&error.length>0){%>
    <div class="alert"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill"></i><%=error%></div>
  <%}%>
  <form method="POST" action="/livreur/login">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Votre numéro de téléphone</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <i class="bi bi-telephone"></i>
        <input type="tel" name="telephone" placeholder="6XX XXX XXX" required autofocus/>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
      <label>Mot de passe</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <i class="bi bi-lock"></i>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Votre mot de passe" required/>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> Se connecter</button>
  </form>
  <div class="divider">ou</div>
  <div class="info-box">
    <i class="bi bi-whatsapp" style="color:#25D366;font-size:16px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"></i>
    <span>Votre restaurant peut vous envoyer un <strong>lien d'accès direct</strong> par WhatsApp — aucun mot de passe requis.</span>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
